Author: jayrambling
Text: It's sooo stressful and she only told me yesterday. I'm freaking out trying to get all of the details from her but she doesn't know about my ED so it's a bit difficult to ask questions without her thinking something is up

Author: hemp_heart
Text: I feel you. Plans that revolve around eating must be totally set in stone or I will have a mental breakdown. I get so upset if things change because I would've spent all day--maybe even week--prepping for said plans.
